  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Sparks strike from these boots whenever they touch the ground, increasing in number as the wearer gathers speed.</em></p><p><strong>1st Level:</strong> While you wear these boots, any weapon ability that deals rolled damage using your unarmed strikes deals an extra [[/damage 1 lightning]] damage. Additionally, you gain a +2 bonus to speed.</p><p><strong>5th Level:</strong> The extra lightning damage granted by the treads increases to [[/damage 2 lightning]]. Additionally, for each square you move on your turn before you use a weapon ability that deals rolled damage using your unarmed strikes, this extra damage increases by 1 (to a maximum of 4).</p><p><strong>9th Level:</strong> The extra lightning damage granted by the treads increases to [[/damage 3 lightning]], and your movement can increase that extra damage to a maximum of 6. Additionally, you can use a maneuver to perform a flying lightning kick on one adjacent creature. That target is pushed up to 5 squares, and you can move to any square adjacent to the target after the push.</p>",
